            </arrangement>
            <scopecontent id="aspace_8bad659c73d260f8f7969e57f04adb61">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Three published autobiographical works are represented by holograph drafts: <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                     <part>Le bonhomme de neige</part>
                  </title>, <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                     <part>Origines du coeur</part>
                  </title>, and <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                     <part>Le statue de sel</part>
                  </title>. Holograph drafts are also present for several short stories, as well as unidentified writings, and fragments. Journals for 1914-1915 document Moreno's nursing work in a military hospital in Nice. Writings of others consist mostly of unidentified poems and play fragments.</p>
            </scopecontent>
